	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I recently acquired one of these and I have been to Chris Covell's page about this unit, but I want to know if anyone here can answer the following :
<br />
<br />1. this unit seems to play cartridge games at a slow speed. is this normal?
<br />2. what do I need to convert .NES format games to work on this unit?
<br />3. what memory mappers does this unit support?
<br />4. does there exist a way to use regular NES controllers with this unit?
<br />
<br />any help is appreciated!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


